Solution 1: Pre-format cells

Select the cells where you'll enter probabilities

Right-click > "Format Cells"

Choose "Number" category

Set decimal places to 4

Now enter your 0.1667 values

A bus shows up at a bus stop every 20 minutes. If you arrive at the bus stop, what is the probability that the bus will show up in 8 minutes or less?

Solution:

a: 0 minutes
b: 20 minutes
x1: 0 minutes
x2: 8 minutes

https://i.postimg.cc/fbj5dz3C/image.png

The probability that the bus shows up in 8 minutes or less is 0.4.

